file.title: Untitled
file.preview:
Hello Sir, 

I would like to bring one issue to your notice which i have been facing from last many years as being the 3 customer. I normally do monthly top up of 20€ to avail the data plan credit every month. For this I use the recurring option on 3 website to setup the top up. I have tried many different way to make sure that the topup happens before the 30 days finish. I selected 28th or each month, 1st of each month etc. 

Now I would like to tell you the scenario where is the issue is happening. Let say i set the top up date 28th of each month, that means my plan cycle will be 28th to 28th (or it will change to 27th depend on number of days in the month) and because of that sometimes i have to pay for that 1 day which because the 30days finish already. In my understanding the recurring option either should have better explaination or better facitily for the customer for topping up before the plans ends. The recurring for me is be free of any worry when the plans end when to turn off the internet etc....
